程序包 projecttwo

类 GymManager

java.lang.Object
projecttwo.GymManager
public class GymManager extends Object
This class is for the running of a Gym. Given commands can either add, delete, or print a list of members Given commands can also add, delete, or print a list of classes for members
作者:
Kangwei Zhu, Michael Israel

  • 构造器详细资料

    • GymManager

      public GymManager()
      Default constructor.

  • 方法详细资料

    • run

      public void run()
      The method is used when the gym starts for the day. Given commands can either add, delete, or print a list of members Given commands can also add, delete, or print a list of classes for members

    • addClasses

      private void addClasses()
      The method is used to add all classes the gym offers to the database.

    • A

      private void A(String[] cmdLine)
      The method is used when adding a member to the database.
      参数:
      cmdLine - Takes in location, dob, full name, and expire date of an individual

    • R

      private void R(String[] cmdLine)
      The method is used when removing a member to the database.
      参数:
      cmdLine - Takes in dob and full name of a member

    • P

      private void P()
      The method is used when printing/displaying a list of members in database.

    • PC

      private void PC()
      The method is used to display the list of members in the database. Ordered by the county names and then the zip codes; that is, if the locations are in the same county, ordered by the zip codes.

    • PN

      private void PN()
      The method is used to display the list of members in the database. Ordered by the members’ last names and then first names; that is, if two members have the same last name, ordered by the first name.

    • PD

      private void PD()
      The method is used to display the list of members in the database ordered by the expiration dates. If two expiration dates are the same, their order doesn’t matter.

    • S

      private void S()
      The method is used to display the fitness class schedule. A fitness class shall include the fitness class name, instructor’s name, the time of the class, and the list of members who have already checked in today

    • C

      private void C(String[] cmdLine)
      The method is used for members to check in to a fitness class. Not allowed to be added if --> the membership has expired, the member does not exist, the date of birth is invalid, the fitness class does not exist, there is a time conflict with other fitness classes, or the member has already checked in
      参数:
      cmdLine - Takes in class name, dob, and full name of a member

    • D

      private void D(String[] cmdLine)
      The method is used to drop the fitness classes after the member checked in to a class. Will not allow the member to drop the class if the member is not checked in, the date of birth is invalid, or the fitness class does not exist.

    • isValidLocation

      private boolean isValidLocation(String loc)
      The method is used to see if a fitness class located at a location.
      参数:
      loc - The location of a fitness class
      返回:
      true if there is a fitness class located at the location. false otherwise
